com.github.wuic.nut

Class TransformedNut

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.wuic.nut.AbstractNut
      • com.github.wuic.nut.NutWrapper
        • com.github.wuic.nut.TransformedNut
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConvertibleNut, Nut, Serializable

    public class TransformedNut
extends NutWrapper
implements Serializable

    A transformed nut wraps a ConvertibleNut and considers its input stream as the result of the transformation. Consequently, not transformers will be used and no changes of the state will be accepted.

    The instances could be serialized so the wrapped nut must be a Serializable.

    Since:
    0.5.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Guillaume DROUET
